item.title: Help
item.dc:creator: @T41 t4
item.description:
@T41 wrote:

Uhm, create a zip archive of your classes making sure you unpack and load your cache from user.home and include a manifest in the archive that points to the main class. Rename the archive’s extension to jar, sign the jar, upload to a webserver with an html page which executes the applet?

Must be a pretty piss poor project if you’re incapable of doing that…
